Rules:

==========SCORING===========

------- Rivers -------
 - Fisherman: 1 x segment + 1 x fish in ponds at ends of stream
 - Hut: 1 x every fish in pond connected to river system

------- Meadows -------
 - Hunter: 2 x animal in meadow
        Each tiger subtracts one dear instead of giving two points

------- Forests -------
 - Gatherer: 2 x forest segment + 2 x each segment with mushrooms
         If completed forest contains gold nugget, draw a gold nugget card and play it immediately. You may also play a meeple or hut on it when placed.
